{
  "subject": "Proposal for Mobile App UI Design",
  "body": "<p>Hi Alex Johnson,</p><p>I’m excited about the opportunity to design a modern, intuitive UI for your fitness tracking app. With over 4 years of experience in React Native and UI/UX design, I have successfully delivered high‑impact mobile interfaces for clients like FitLife (5‑star rating) and ShopEasy (4.8‑star rating).</p><p>Given the project scope and a 3‑week deadline, I propose a competitive hourly rate of $34‑$36, which is below the market average of $38.5/hr while still reflecting my proven expertise. This rate would bring the total estimated cost to approximately $5,100–$5,400 for the full project.</p><p>I’m ready to start immediately and can provide a detailed project plan within the next 24 hours. Let me know if you’d like to discuss further or schedule a quick call.</p><p>Best regards,<br/>Jane Doe<br/><a href=\"https://myportfolio.com/jane\">Portfolio</a><br/>Rate: $45/hr (current), proposed: $34‑$36/hr</p>"
}
